{{title 'Select Plugins'}}
<h1>Select Plugins</h1>

<p>Some plugins are optional, and can be easily disabled and enabled.  Please read the <a href="https://aresmush.com/tutorials/config/plugins/">Enabling and Disabling Plugins</a> tutorial to learn more.</p>

<div class="alert alert-warning"><b>Note!</b> Only plugins marked 'optional' below can safely be disabled without making custom code changes.  Any plugin can be removed; but you have to take care with required ones.  See the tutorial above for more information.</div>
  
<table>
{{#each model as |plugin|}}

<tr>
  <td><span class="text">{{plugin.name}}</span></td>
  <td>
  {{input type='checkbox' checked=plugin.selected}} 
  </td>

  <td>
  {{#if plugin.optional}}
  <span class="label label-success">optional</span>
  {{else}}
  <span class="label label-warning">required</span>
  {{/if}}
  </td>
</tr>
  

{{/each}}

</table>


<div class="row">
    <div class="col col-xs-12">
        <div class="pull-right">
          {{#link-to 'setup' class="btn btn-default"}}Cancel{{/link-to}}

          <button {{action 'save'}} class="btn btn-primary">Save</button>
          
         </div>
  </div>
</div>


{{outlet}}